If something happens already, it happens before a certain time.

01:52:28.640 --> 01:52:31.680
It is already time for the movie to start.

01:52:31.680 --> 01:52:32.560
Let's go in.

01:52:34.720 --> 01:52:35.200
Basic

01:52:36.320 --> 01:52:39.520
