01:52:40.720 --> 01:52:43.840
I learned some basic English skills in school today.

01:52:46.000 --> 01:52:46.240
Bit

01:52:47.440 --> 01:52:49.520
A bit is a small amount of something.

01:52:50.640 --> 01:52:53.760
