01:52:55.840 --> 01:52:56.400
Consider

01:52:57.520 --> 01:52:59.920
To consider something means to think about it.

01:53:00.880 --> 01:53:04.640
Be didn't like his job, be consider getting a new one.

01:53:06.800 --> 01:53:07.440
Destroy

01:53:08.480 --> 01:53:13.040
To destroy means to damage something so badly that it cannot be used.

01:53:14.160 --> 01:53:15.840
The glass was destroyed.

01:53:17.920 --> 01:53:18.560
Entertain

01:53:19.600 --> 01:53:22.720
To entertain someone is to do something that they enjoy.

01:53:23.920 --> 01:53:26.560
The clown entertained the kids at the party.

01:53:28.640 --> 01:53:29.120
Extra

01:53:30.240 --> 01:53:33.040
If something is extra, it is more than what is needed.

01:53:34.080 --> 01:53:36.800
The squirrel had extra nuts for the winter.

01:53:38.960 --> 01:53:39.360
Goal

01:53:40.480 --> 01:53:42.240
A goal is something you work toward.

01:53:43.440 --> 01:53:45.600
Her goal was to become a doctor.

01:53:47.760 --> 01:53:48.160
Lie

01:53:49.280 --> 01:53:52.960
To lie is to say or write something untrue to deceive someone.

01:53:54.080 --> 01:53:57.680
Whenever Pinocchio lied to his father, his nose grew.

01:54:00.000 --> 01:54:00.320
Meat

01:54:01.520 --> 01:54:03.120
Meat is food made of animals.

01:54:04.320 --> 01:54:07.200
This piece of meat I'm eating tastes very good.

01:54:09.360 --> 01:54:09.840
Opinion

01:54:10.960 --> 01:54:13.680
An opinion is a thought about a person or a thing.

01:54:14.960 --> 01:54:17.120
