01:54:17.840 --> 01:54:19.600
She said it was not funny.

01:54:21.760 --> 01:54:22.080
Real

01:54:23.280 --> 01:54:26.000
If something is real, it actually exists.

01:54:26.960 --> 01:54:30.240
The handbag has a stamp on it so it's real.

01:54:32.400 --> 01:54:32.960
Reflect

01:54:34.000 --> 01:54:37.040
To reflect is when a surface sends back light,

01:54:37.040 --> 01:54:38.960
heat, sound, or an image.

01:54:40.000 --> 01:54:42.640
Her face was reflected on the smooth glass.

01:54:44.880 --> 01:54:45.440
Regard

01:54:46.480 --> 01:54:50.400
To regard someone or something is to think of them in a certain way.

01:54:51.600 --> 01:54:54.320
